<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="61" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="61">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="61">Panicle dense, compact, with short branches. The erect spikelets seem to be sessile. Awns more or less divaricate at maturity.</paragraph>
