<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="61">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="61">
Southern Europe, temperate Asia and North Africa. Etymology: Named from the Latin 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“penicillus”">&quot;penicillus&quot;</normalizedToken>
